Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:04.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pale broken wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.76,0:00:12.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are just a bit tired from\Nthat clear blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:17.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to force\Nyour smiles for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:24.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now... to smile for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:29.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Loneliness still continues to stalk me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:32.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A candle lit within
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:36.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The party is lively;\Nthe chandeliers are gorgeous, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:43.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I fill the hole left behind\Nby those lacking words?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:46.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:53.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can at least swim freely\Nin my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:56.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't need a sky like that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:01:06.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can face tomorrow without painting\Nover all the things up to yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:10.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pale broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.32,0:01:17.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are just a bit tired from\Nthat clear blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:22.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to force\Nyour smiles for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:29.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now... to smile for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:41.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:46.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:48.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:51.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you're alive\Nmeans it's a win.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:53.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:58.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were me,\Nyou wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:02.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimmjow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:16.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Grimmjow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:20.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:23.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have some words\Nof apology to share?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimmjow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:27.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:29.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:35.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Kaname.\NBesides, I'm not angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:36.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Aizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:43.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimmjow's recent actions are\Nthe manifestation of deep loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:50.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that so? Grimmjow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:55.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:00.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:01.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tosen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:08.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Aizen!\NPlease authorize his execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:11.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:14.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's personal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:17.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't like me,\Nthat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:21.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the way a Director General\Nshould act?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:26.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my belief that those who\Ndisrupt harmony must not be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:27.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:31.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For the organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:34.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For Lord Aizen's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:39.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! You're so good at making\Na case for the cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:42.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's a noble cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:46.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And your actions show\Nno cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:51.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice without a cause is...\Nnothing more than killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:56.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, killing in the name\Nof a cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...is justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:10.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hado 54...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Haien!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:16.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:18.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:24.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!\NYou cut off my arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:27.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimmjow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:34.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you attack Kaname right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:39.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will no longer be able\Nto forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:17.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing with your subordinate again?\NYou're not nice, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:19.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:21.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew from the start that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:28.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,if you say such things\Nin front of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kaname would do that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:35.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:39.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And we even lost five Arrancars...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:47.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They were only low-class Gillians.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:51.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no change in our plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:57.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If we ready top-class Vasto Lordes\Nand complete the Espada...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:02.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...there will be no foe in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The resonance of Spiritual Pressure\Nhas stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:17.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:25.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:30.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you so worried about\Nthe Soul Reapers and their fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:35.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I'm concerned about is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:40.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,whether my powers will really return\Nwith a method like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:42.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:44.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:48.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In this secret room,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:50.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,made from Spiritualized Silver\Nand Spiritualized Glass,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:53.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep countering your arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:56.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing something like this\Nover and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:02.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it truly return\Nmy Quincy powers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:09.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:16.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:32.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:36.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat! Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:39.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat... Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:52.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here. Dad!\NBrother's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:54.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:56.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What about Rukia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia is gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:04.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're okay, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:11.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother is gone!\NDo you know where he went, Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:12.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:19.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're better already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:26.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- It healed at an unbelievable speed.\N- I'm so glad, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:27.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:30.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:31.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep getting better and better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:37.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, that's not true at all.\NI'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:40.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you healed, Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:43.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:53.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel responsible\Nfor my injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:55.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being so full of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:59.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One's injury is caused\Nby one's error.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:02.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that weak to be protected\Nby the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:05.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So stop looking so grim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:08.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:16.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Hollow within you.\NWhy not ask Urahara about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who trained you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:23.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he might perhaps know\Nabout the inner Hollow within you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:27.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like asking\NMr. Urahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:34.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he already senses\Nwhat's happening to me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And if he knew the way\Nto resolve it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:44.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm sure he'd have taught it to me\Nbefore I went to Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:52.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That means even he doesn't know\Nhow to suppress this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He trained me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:59.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:06.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So...I don't want to keep\Nquestioning him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:17.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo... Where have you gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:20.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:01.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...\NIt's no good...like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:08.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm... Looking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:12.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's what you call\Nwifely assistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:15.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even understand\Nwhat that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:17.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:22.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, err...Thanks, Sis...\Nfor taking care of my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:26.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. No problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:28.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like,\Nyou can stay here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:40.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you mean "love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:45.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:48.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. A lonely man\Nwho doesn't know love
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:51.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,should be enveloped\Nwith unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of woman\NI want to become.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:11:57.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, dedicate your life to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:01.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing!\NI have to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:02.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Keigo! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:08.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run. Keigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:15.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my... So many are absent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:20.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, Kurosaki, Kuchiki, Sado...\NThese guys again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they up to lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:28.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm sure Kurosaki and the others\Nwon't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:30.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:33.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:42.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's start class!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess...who!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:58.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea, Matsumoto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:02.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Captain,\Nyou got it right the first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would get it wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:09.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:14.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, kids in uniform\Nhave to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My report!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:20.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That it was easy thanks to\Nthe Gentei Kaijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:23.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys were small fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:26.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't Vasto Lordes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:30.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor were they Adjuchas,\Nthe rank below that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:35.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even we of captain rank couldn't\Ndefeat Gillians
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:37.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,without our Gentei Kaijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:43.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how strong they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:47.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:52.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon Ururu! Get with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:54.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think we're doing this for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For you! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:57.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:02.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your injury is healed, so look happier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:07.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I... I just got better and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:08.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of want to be left alone\Nto recuperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:09.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oomph! You need oomph!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:15.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:19.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My arm hurts...Jinta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:20.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:23.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- It hurts!\N- I think we should leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:25.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Urahara...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:35.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Sado. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:40.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...! Please train me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:42.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:47.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be on the test,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:48.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- so take notes now, got it?\N- I wonder what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Let's start with page 43.\N- to Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:28.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you knew where we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:44.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That face looks like you've finally\Ndecided to become one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:48.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so bad at detecting\NSpiritual Pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:51.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you found this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:56.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I figured you'd come,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:59.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so I released a whole lot of\NSpiritual Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:01.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to make it easier for you to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:10.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your coming here means that\Nyou've decided to join us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:14.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:15.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:18.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:26.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kid yourself! I'm here to\Ntake advantage of you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't join you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want you to show me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:37.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,how to suppress the Hollow inside me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure take us lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:44.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd teach you, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:45.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get it outta you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:48.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:52.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,By force!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:54.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:07.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What a difficult fellow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:31.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:56.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy named Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:18:00.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not bad,\Nholding his own against Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:02.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid, look again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:06.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji isn't serious at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:13.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like Ichigo\Nis fighting seriously either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:16.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite obvious that he's nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:20.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nervous about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:21.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid is fighting scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:28.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's nervous about releasing\Nhis inner Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:35.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the level the kid\Nwe're trying to recruit is at.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:44.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are you going, Hiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:48.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi... Put up five more barriers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:58.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:00.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:10.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, put up five more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:13.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But...I couldn't do it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, let me say one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:23.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got this all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:24.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:29.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true we're trying to recruit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:33.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's not something\Nfor you to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:36.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:40.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The power to choose is on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:44.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you want to join, or not...\NThat's not the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:47.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We look at your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:53.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's whether\Nwe really want you or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:55.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:19:59.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about your position carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:02.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have the right to choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:05.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have the power,\Nwe will make you one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:08.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll teach you how to\Nsuppress your Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:12.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you have no power,\Nwho cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:15.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll disappear to wherever,\Nbecome a Hollow,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:16.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and die a shameful death!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:24.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you understand,\Nchange to a Hollow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:26.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll take a look\Nat your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:29.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:32.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not too bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:35.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have the right\Nto choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:36.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:43.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Change to a Hollow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:48.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're scared and\Ndon't want to change,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:49.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,then it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:55.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll directly drag out...\Nthe Hollow inside you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:58.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,With force!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:03.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:05.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:06.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:12.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's scaring you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:15.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A mask doesn't\Nmake you a Visored!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:16.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course\Nwe can change into Hollows!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:19.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be scared, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:23.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not nice like Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.07,0:21:27.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't change into a Hollow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:39.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:46.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...will really die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:54.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I dressed up my five fingers\Nwith a manicure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:22:00.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And then what's glowing\Nwas me instead
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:03.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspiration is like a goldfish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.56,0:22:06.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps a voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:09.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no sound that\Ndoesn't bounce back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:25.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those lines stretching parallel\Nto each other
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:31.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They say one line turns beautiful,\Nthen deteriorate repeatedly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.48,0:22:36.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm standing right there, \Nbut the way is locked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:40.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The distance grows, \Nbut it's within reach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:41.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And even today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:51.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I trace your gibberish roman letters\Nover and over with my left hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:23:01.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The one you see the moment\Nyou open your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:11.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What color will\Nhe paint your nails?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:22.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This secret room built inside\Nthe hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.85,0:23:24.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When was it built?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:29.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a slight change in the blueprint\Nand built it secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:30.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure doing something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:32.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't compromise\Nthe building's sturdiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:34.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is important...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:37.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers\N- Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:40.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good! I don't know why,\Nbut I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:42.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:45.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:50.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But when the gauge of\NVermillion Hisagomaru is not full,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.37,0:23:51.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it's really weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.81,0:23:53.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes it is!\N- Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.52,0:23:59.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that, kid. You're not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.76,0:24:02.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Play with me!